name: Anna Louise
description:
A request of @neven.

Anna Louise is a model, Youtuber and social media personality.

1500-step trained on a dataset of 20 images with my usual settings. I did reduce the learning rate after step 1000 to 0.001, though.

Curious about my work process? I have summarized it here.

Appreciate my work? My TIs are free, but you can always buy me a coffee. :)
